ung](#tab2)\nn.A.\n[Zutaten](#tab3)\nn.A.", "language": null, "image": "https://www.ayurveda-paradies.ch/cdn/shop/products/wie-neu-geboren-durch-modernes-ayurveda-ayurveda-paradies-schweiz-879419_1200x1200.jpg?v=1690283596", "pagetype": "product", "links": ["/collections", "https://www.ayurveda-paradies.ch", "/collections", "#", "/collections/ayurveda-ole-ab-200ml", "/collections/massage-zubehor", "/collections/spezialoele-balsam-ghee", "#", "/products/ayurveda-premium-gold-krautertee-fur-vata", "/products/ayurveda-premium-gold-krautertee-fur-vata", "/products/ayurveda-premium-gold-krautertee-fur-vata", "/products/ayurveda-premium-gold-aktiv-f-frauentee", "/products/ayurveda-premium-gold-manner-aktivtee", "/collections/tee", "/collections/ayurveda-kaffee-ersatz", "#", "/collections/gewurze", "/collections/gewurzmischungen", "/collections/salze", "/collections/vollrohrzucker", "#", "/collections/duschmittel-duschgel", "/collections/gesichtspflege-1", "/collections/haarpflege", "/collections/hand-fusspflege-1", "/collections/korperpflege", "/collections/mund-zahne", "/collections/nasenpflege", "/collections/naturkosmetik", "/collections/seifen", "#", "/collections/fruchtmus", "/collections/ayurveda-gritham-gudham-lehyam-kwath", "/collections/pulver-churna-choornam", "/collections/nahrungserganzungen", "/collections/ayurveda-bucher", "/collections/spirituelle-bucher", "/collections/accessoires", "/collections/trinkflaschen", "", "https://www.ayurveda-paradies.ch/blogs/magazin/ayurveda-ausbildungen-und-weiterbildungen", "/blogs/magazin", "/pages/qualitaetssicherung", "/pages/team", "#", "https://www.ayurveda-paradies.ch/a/self-faq", "https://www.ayurveda-paradies.ch/pages/kontakt-willkommen-im-ayurveda-paradies", "https://www.ayurveda-paradies.ch/pages/grosshandel", "/collections", "#", "/collections/ayurveda-ole-ab-200ml", "/collections/massage-zubehor", "/collections/spezialoele-balsam-ghee", "#", "/products/ayurveda-premium-gold-krautertee-fur-vata", "/products/ayurv